{"id":"d-50e4ea3024c7459092e96b17c2895dc3","name":"PickupEmail","generation":"dynamic","updated_at":"2022-12-03 21:01:40","versions":[{"id":"43beeecb-9bfd-49a4-b8b4-4085ff887001","user_id":22059782,"template_id":"d-50e4ea3024c7459092e96b17c2895dc3","active":1,"name":"Clone: 1.0 2022-12-03T21:01:39.689Z","html_content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n\r\n<html lang=\"en\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\r\n  <head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\r\n    <title>{{{subject}}}</title>\r\n    <style>\r\n        body{\r\n          font-size: medium;\r\n          font-family: 'Poppins';\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .mainContainer{\r\n            padding-left: 4%;\r\n            padding-right: 4%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .paragraphs{\r\n            margin-top:12px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .sectionHeader{\r\n            margin-top:24px;margin-bottom:8px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        button{\r\n          color: #fff;\r\n          background-color: #96ba00;         \r\n          border-radius:5px ;\r\n          font-style: normal;\r\n          font-weight: 500;\r\n          font-size: 15px;\r\n          line-height: 22.5px; \r\n          border: none;\r\n          outline: none;        \r\n          height: 45px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        a{\r\n          color: #96ba00;\r\n          background-color: transparent;         \r\n        }\r\n\r\n        table{\r\n          margin-bottom: 1rem;         \r\n        }\r\n\r\n        tr,th,td{\r\n          padding: 0.5rem;\r\n          border: none;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        td,th{\r\n          width: 25%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        th{\r\n          background-color: #EAEFF6;\r\n          text-align: left;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        tr{\r\n          background-color: #F8F9FA;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .closingNotification{\r\n          font-size: small;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .closingLogo{\r\n            max-height: 40px;\r\n            margin-left: -15px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .emailHeaderContainer{\r\n            box-shadow: 0 .5rem 1rem rgba(0,0,0,.15);\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            max-height: 200px;\r\n        }\r\n        \r\n         .emailHeaderContainer > table, tr, th{\r\n            background-color:#fff;\r\n            border-collapse: collapse;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .logoSlogan{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            flex-direction: column;\r\n            padding:1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;\r\n            width: 50%;           \r\n\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .globeContainer{\r\n            width: 46.97%;\r\n            text-align: right;            \r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .bannerGlobe{\r\n            width:100%;\r\n            height: 100%;\r\n            margin-right: -25%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .bannerHeading{\r\n            margin-left:3rem;\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n  </head>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <div class=\"emailHeaderContainer\">\r\n      <!--<div class=\"logoSlogan\">-->\r\n      <!--    <img src=\"http://cdn.mcauto-images-production.sendgrid.net/3980f70febc70fb8/f043a16f-bf05-44d1-b9f6-b71d80833810/412x59.png\" alt=\"TrashMob.eco logo\" class=\"bannerLogo\">-->\r\n      <!--    <h3 class=\"bannerHeading\">Meet up. Clean up. Feel good.</h3>-->\r\n      <!--</div>-->\r\n      <!--<div class=\"globeContainer\">-->\r\n      <!--    <img src=\"http://cdn.mcauto-images-production.sendgrid.net/3980f70febc70fb8/ab3e061e-8542-4c35-acb0-87b4ab497504/407x224.png\" class=\"bannerGlobe\" alt=\"Globe\">-->\r\n      <!--</div>      -->\r\n          <table>\r\n    <tr style=\"background-color:white\">\r\n    <td>\r\n    <img src=\"http://cdn.mcauto-images-production.sendgrid.net/3980f70febc70fb8/f043a16f-bf05-44d1-b9f6-b71d80833810/412x59.png\" alt=\"TrashMob.eco logo\" class=\"bannerLogo\">\r\n          <h3 class=\"bannerHeading\" style=\"margin-left:2%\">Meet up. Clean up. Feel good.</h3>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td style=\"margin-left:70%\">\r\n    <img src=\"http://cdn.mcauto-images-production.sendgrid.net/3980f70febc70fb8/ab3e061e-8542-4c35-acb0-87b4ab497504/407x224.png\" class=\"bannerGlobe\" alt=\"Globe\">\r\n    </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n    </div>\r\n      <div class=\"mainContainer\">\r\n    <p>Hi,</p>\r\n    <div>\r\n      <p class='paragraphs'>\r\n        {{{emailCopy}}}\r\n      </p>\r\n      <p>\r\n        <b>Event:</b> <a href=\"{{{eventDetailsUrl}}}\">{{{eventName}}}</a>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <p>\r\n        <b><a href=\"{{{eventSummaryUrl}}}\">View Event Summary</a>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <table>\r\n        <tr>\r\n        <th>Location</th>\r\n        <th>Photo</th>\r\n        <th>Notes</th>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        {{#each pickupSpots}}\r\n        <tr>\r\n          <td><a href=\"{{{this.GoogleMapsUrl}}}\">{{{this.StreetAddress}}}</a></td>          \r\n          <td><img width=\"100\" height=\"100\" src=\"{{{this.ImageUrl}}}\" /></td>          \r\n          <td>{{{this.Notes}}}</td>          \r\n        </tr>\r\n        {{/each}}\r\n      </table>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top:36px;\">\r\n      <p>Thanks,</p>\r\n      <p>The team at TrashMob.eco.</p>\r\n      <img src=\"http://cdn.mcauto-images-production.sendgrid.net/3980f70febc70fb8/f043a16f-bf05-44d1-b9f6-b71d80833810/412x59.png\" alt=\"TrashMob.eco logo\" class=\"closingLogo\">\r\n      <p class=\"closingNotification\">\r\n        <a href='<%asm_group_unsubscribe_raw_url%>'>Click here</a> to manage your notification preferences for TrashMob.eco.\r\n      </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>\r\n","plain_content":"Meet up. Clean up. Feel good.\n-----------------------------\n\nHi,\n\n{{{emailCopy}}}\n\n*Event:* {{{eventName}}} ( {{{eventDetailsUrl}}} )\n\n*View Event Summary ( {{{eventSummaryUrl}}} )*\n\n*{{#each pickupSpots}} {{/each}}\n\nLocation Photo Notes {{{this.StreetAddress}}} ( {{{this.GoogleMapsUrl}}} ) {{{this.Notes}}}\n\n*\n*\n\nThanks,\n\nThe team at TrashMob.eco.\n\nClick here ( <%asm_group_unsubscribe_raw_url%> ) to manage your notification preferences for TrashMob.eco.\n\n*\n**","generate_plain_content":true,"subject":"{{{subject}}}","updated_at":"2023-05-21 22:01:48","editor":"code","test_data":"{\n    \"subject\" : \"A Trashmob.eco Event has pickups ready!\",\n    \"emailCopy\": \"Hey, there are some pickups!\",\n    \"username\" : \"Helpful Partner\",\n    \"eventName\" : \"Test Event\",    \n    \"eventDetailsUrl\": \"https://www.trashmob.eco/eventdetails/1234\",\n    \"eventSummaryUrl\": \"https://www.trashmob.eco/eventsummary/1234\",\n    \"pickupSpots\": [\n        { \"GoogleMapsUrl\": \"https://maps.google.com\", \"ImageUrl\":\"https://www.trashmob.eco/TrashMobEco_CircleLogo.png\", \"StreetAddress\": \"123 Anystreet\", \"Notes\": \"Pile sitting by the stoplight\" },\n        { \"GoogleMapsUrl\": \"https://maps.google.com\", \"ImageUrl\":\"https://www.trashmob.eco/TrashMobEco_CircleLogo.png\", \"StreetAddress\": \"128 Anystreet\", \"Notes\": \"Huge pile under the boardwalk\" }        \n        ]\n}","thumbnail_url":"//us-east-2-production-thumbnail-bucket.s3.amazonaws.com/8fd35cec2e38e480055b62b879a0da60269da1acbaadbcd42bc8ae9a225b7a18.png"}]}
